'''Miguel Sapochnik''' is a British director of film and television and former storyboard artist. He is best known as the director of the feature film ''[[wikipedia:Repo Men|Repo Man]]''. His most notable television credits are ''[[wikipedia:House M.D. (TV Series)|House M.D.]]'', ''[[wikipedia:Fringe (TV Series)|Fringe]]'', ''[[wikipedia:Awake (TV Series)|Awake]]'', and ''[[wikipedia:Mind Games (TV Series)|Mind Games]]''.

On July 15, 2014, it was announced that Sapochnik will be directing two episodes in the [[Season 5|fifth season]], the seventh and eighth episodes.&lt;ref&gt;[http://winteriscoming.net/2014/07/15/directors-game-thrones-season-5-announced/]&lt;/ref&gt;
